- title('Locations')
extends ../layout-2013

block body

  - activeNav = "locations"
  include ../index/_header-mini

  .inner-page.container
    .row
      .col-lg-8.col-sm-8.col-md-8
        .locations
          :markdown
            Locations
            =========

            _Contestants may compete "virtually" from anywhere in the world_, but
            [Joyent] will be hosting Knockout HQ in San Francisco and several groups worldwide have graciously organized space for
            contestants to work from, meet up, and have an awesome time.

            <a name="sf"></a>
            San Francisco
            -------------

            NKO HQ is setting up at [Joyent]’s downtown San Francisco office. Doors open
            at 4 PM PST. Duke it out in the ring with your closest Node.js friends.
            We’ll serve up drinks, chow, and a rockin’ good time including ping pong!

            Registration is required to attend (participants / judges only).

            <p class="button">
              <a href="http://nko2013.eventbrite.com/" class="btn btn-primary">Register to attend</a>
            </p>

            <p class="map">
              <iframe width="576" height="324" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" src="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=1+Embarcadero+Center,+9th+Floor,+San+Francisco,+CA+(Knockout+HQ+@+Joyent)&output=embed"></iframe>
            </p>

            <div class="with-popover">
              <p><strong>Get there via Uber. $20 off your first ride. Coupon code: NODEKNOCKOUT13</strong></p>
              <div class="popover-content" style="display:none">
                Up to $20 off a ride for all new riders. Text NodeKnockout13 to 827-222, follow the link to download the app, and create an account. The promotion will be automatically applied when you take your first trip.
              </div>
            </div>

            <hr>

            Other Locations
            ---------------

            Not in San Francisco? Find node.js-loving enthusiasts worldwide.
            **Want to host a satellite location? [Send us a pull request] or [let us
            know].**

            [Joyent]: http://www.joyent.com/
            [Send us a pull request]: https://github.com/nko4/website/blob/master/views/index/locations.jade
            [let us know]: mailto:all@nodeknockout.com

          ul.locations
            // li
              h4#seattle Seattle, WA
              != address('1617 Boylston Ave, Seattle, WA 98122')
              :markdown
                ### [NKO @ Office Nomads]
                ##### 1617 Boylston Ave, Seattle, WA 98122

                [Office Nomads] is hosting the CascadiaJS after-hack!
                Come hang out and code from noon - 6pm on Saturday.
                Contact [@CarterRabasa] if you have any questions.

                [Office Nomads]: http://officenomads.com/
                [NKO @ Office Nomads]: http://officenomads.com/
                [@end33r]: http://twitter.com/carterrabasa

            // li
              h4#paris Paris, France
              != address('100 Rue de la folie mericourt, Paris, France')
              :markdown
                ### [Joshfire]
                ##### 100 Rue de la folie mericourt, Paris, France

                [Joshfire] will be hosting teams and onlookers, then party to celebrate
                Node and French house music.

                [Joshfire]: http://www.joshfire.com/

            // li
              h4#taipei Taipei, Taiwan
              != address('台北市南港區研究院路二段128號', 'maps.google.com.tw')
              :markdown
                ### [Node.js 台灣社群][1]
                ##### 台北市南港區研究院路二段128號

                歡迎各位 Node.js 開發者一起參與，共同奮戰 48
                小時，活動時間台北時間，11/10  08:00 - 11/11 20:00

                Register at [Node KO 台灣活動網站][2] or contact [@NodejsTaiwan].

