              h4#warsaw Warsaw, Poland
              != address('Pokrzywnicka 3A, Warsaw, Poland')
              :markdown
                ### [Node.js Weekend]
                ##### Pokrzywnicka 3A, Warsaw, Poland

                [Node.js Weekend] will be the host for the Warsaw event - come and enjoy
